text: Ellen Van Dijk finishes first in Waregem. The eighth running of Dwars door Vlaanderen's women's race was held on Wednesday 3 April 2019. The race started in Tielt and finished in Waregem, covering a distance of 118 km. ==Teams== 25 teams competed in the race.
